data.description: Check out this beautiful home located in the quiet, established neighborhood of Forest Hills in Gladewater ISD!! This home features gorgeous custom-built cabinetry throughout the kitchen and living areas, beautiful granite countertops, and an open floorplan. The sizable sunroom is a great bonus room and can be used for an additional living area, game room, formal dining room, or whatever your heart desires! Outside is where the real fun is located with the heated in-ground pool, hot tub, and cabana! All outdoor furniture, pool storage boxes, and other items located outside will convey with the property, as well. Schedule a tour of this amazing home today!!
